data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4 bdrm, 2 1/2 bath home! With a little over 2400 sqft, & abundant storage space, this home has alot to offer! FRESHLY PAINTED INTERIOR ON THE MAIN LEVEL! On the main floor there is LR, formal DR, Kitchen w/plenty of cabinets & a lg storage space perfect for a pantry, den/office w/french doors, primary bdrm w/full bath, new ldry & new half bath. Upstairs you'll find 3 lg bedrooms w/walk-in closets, & another full bath. The partial bsmnt is great for storage, and there is also an enclosed back porch. The newer 24 x 40 attached garage is a great BONUS and ready to custom fit your needs! There is an additional storage building as well. Conveniently located on a corner lot close to churches, banking, retail, and the heart of Downtown Rensselaer! All measurements and square footage are not a guarantee, buyer or buyer's agent to verify.
